{"tid":276490,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[第一次]點解可以咁黑？","createTime":"2017-06-09T00:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T00:22:12.000Z","uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"564e237608e8dc7db76cd76e304acaeae6341be8","tid":276490,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"第一次係感情台開post<br />\n呢2個星期真係黑到震<br />\n日日搭小巴排隊<br />\n我總係上唔到車<br />\n即係黎1/2/3架車<br />\n前面就會排左16/32/48個人<br />\n然後我排第一等左10分鐘先有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行去巴士站又係<br />\n搭邊架邊架就會係我面前開走<br />\n幫個fd整電話<br />\n可以係屋企冇啦啦跌爆左隻mon<br />\n買隻新嘅返到黎裝機<br />\n又係壞嘅<br />\n幫第二個fd整ipad<br />\n買嘅零件又係有問題<br />\n搵代購買野<br />\n海外集運寄返黎<br />\n到香港比海關扣關<br />\n原因話係同報關單上寫嘅唔同<br />\n間集運又唔認數<br />\n話係我入面有違禁品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n維修工具咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人扣左2個星期應該都<strong></strong>凍過水了<br />\n唉好黑啊！"},{"pid":"a968f52ddaaf3c591543ecec8c1ea7112e16cd15","tid":276490,"uid":50610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"三哀六旺"},{"pid":"fb92694081293225fddb622cdfef5a70dd83b707","tid":276490,"uid":50610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三哀六旺</blockquote><br />\n衰"},{"pid":"0e27f7bb9053db7b70bb64292912b0ad4277ea09","tid":276490,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"只有衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6191de11c6d6bdf99c7ca12bab5e4760dec42ba","tid":276490,"uid":11911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T00:38:03.000Z","msg":"你個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260071a18c5a4fceee12885cf3fcad4cb0c4900e","tid":276490,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個標題<img